  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Healthwatch England - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_healthwatch_england">Healthwatch England</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_healthwatch_england">Healthwatch England</xref>
 is the independent consumer champion for health and social care in England.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_healthwatch_england">Healthwatch England</xref>
 works with 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_local_healthwatch">Local Healthwatch</xref>
 and:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
advises 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
, English 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authorities</xref>
, 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_improvement">NHS Improvement</xref>
 and the Secretary of State for health.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
has the power to recommend that action is taken by the 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_care_quality_commission">Care Quality Commission</xref>
 (
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_care_quality_commission">CQC</xref>
) when there are concerns about health and social care services.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_healthwatch_england">Healthwatch England</xref>
, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_healthwatch_england">Healthwatch England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.healthwatch.co.uk/what-we-do"
            scope="external"
            format="html">What we do</xref>
.  </p>

